# Run outputs. Regenerable from the committed suite definition, and large —
# a single baseline writes 25 repos x 6 tiers of full build logs.
results/

# Quarantined artifact from the truncated-exclusion bug (contents API capped
# the OSS-Fuzz project list at 1000 of 1366). Kept on disk as a debugging
# record, deliberately not committed: it is a superseded and invalid dataset,
# and a copy in the repository invites someone to sample from it.
pool.json.INVALID-*
*.bak

# What IS committed, and must stay committed — the suite definition:
#   CRITERIA.md            the frozen predicates and protocol
#   build_pool.py          pool construction and deterministic sampling
#   schema.py              tier / failure vocabulary
#   run_suite.py           the runner
#   preflight.py           the freeze gate
#   characterise.py        the descriptive layer
#   pool.json              the eligible population these 25 were drawn from
#   repos.yaml             the frozen sample
#   sample_profile.json    the sample profile
#   SAMPLE_PROFILE.md      its human-readable form
#   baseline.lock          the experiment identity at freeze time
